<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4894374>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Prestonia succo. A. habit; B. calyx, pedicels, and floral bracts; C. sepal, adaxial view, showing the colleter; D. corolla, partially open, showing the anthers and the annular corona; E. anther, dorsal view; F. style head; G. nectary and ovary. (Huamantupa et al. 4079, holotype)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4894374/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

